I thought you know --

00:02:10.480 --> 00:02:13.780
&gt;&gt; Peter S. Onuf: Because I'm the
most blessed of the patriarchs.

00:02:13.780 --> 00:02:15.250
&gt;&gt; Annette Gordon-Reed: Peter
