00:05:19.180 --> 00:05:23.330
that is very self-assured,
confident,

00:05:23.330 --> 00:05:24.920
you might say arrogant in a way.

00:05:24.920 --> 00:05:29.800
But certainly believing that he
had a special place and patriarch

00:05:29.800 --> 00:05:35.660
to us is -- it's a negative
