go away and what he wanted would be

00:41:08.940 --> 00:41:14.030
to have family farms, yeoman
farmers, they would take over.

00:41:14.030 --> 00:41:17.520
But what he wanted people to
model was his ideas about science,

00:41:17.520 --> 00:41:20.220
his ideas about art,
those kinds of things,

00:41:20.220 --> 00:41:27.420
I don't think he saw plantation
life as a that aspect of his life.

00:41:27.420 --> 00:41:32.740 position:56%
It was the exalted, the more exalted
things and not just the institution

00:41:32.740 --> 00:41:35.520
that he thought was going to leave.

00:41:35.520 --> 00:41:36.820
&gt;&gt; Peter S. Onuf: And
one way of thinking

00:41:36.820 --> 00:41:39.700
